{"tid":112871,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日係講女權 只係一種政治正確","createTime":"2017-02-08T13:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T02:10:14.000Z","uid":56792,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e31a8a4c5730b798eeea8c70aa75e1e29f24ebf7","tid":112871,"uid":56792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:33:40.000Z","msg":"係發達國家 所謂女性被剝削係假象<br />\n幾十年前係事實<br />\n但時至今日情況早已逆轉<br />\n但點為之&quot;平等&quot;根本冇定義<br />\n於是班婦權人士繼續無止境咁爭取特權<br />\n發展成今日咁畸形既狀態<br />\n喱個時候想搵番平衝經已太遲<br />\n因為爭取女權已經成為主流意識形態<br />\n任何相左既意見都會被打成歧視、文化倒退<br />\n至此冇人敢公開為男性發聲<br />\n女性繼續以&quot;弱者&quot;既身分手握話語權 <br />\n男性只會繼續被剝削"},{"pid":"00cc03e311d1e042e9e6760d692a8b12c60e7019","tid":112871,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"Trump嘅出現有望消除呢班特權階級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20e67979e30e549adfb1571a18e798f69e921ba","tid":112871,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t4cU-KZPpTI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft4cU-KZPpTI&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=70178ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t4cU-KZPpTI</a><br />\n以前爭取投票權，繼承權都合理，但今時今日3th feminism 根本係對男性壓迫，仇視"},{"pid":"55bfafb0d9fd81fc312da7b800b604f81602c1ef","tid":112871,"uid":56792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/t4cU-KZPpTI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft4cU-KZPpTI&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=70178ea6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t4cU-KZPpTI</a><br />\n以前爭取投票權，繼承權都合理，但今時今日3th feminism 根本係對男性壓迫，仇視</blockquote><br />\n第一次睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ad515d1cb97ad335e6a7069c98d450d6aef945","tid":112871,"uid":56792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy